ISLAMABAD, Aug 11 (APP): Pakistan Electronic Media Regulatory Authority ( PEMRA) on Tuesday issued Pakistan’s first teleport licence to Telenest (SMC) Pvt Ltd.
Chairman PEMRA Saleem Baig issued Teleport License to Chief Executive Officer Telenest Mehdi Raza during an event held here at PEMRA headquarters.
